object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
SELECT
bls.batch_id,
bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
AND bls.batch_id = (
SELECT MAX(batch_id)
FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
)
)
SELECT DISTINCT
mtl_apu.source_name,
mtl_apu.load_type,
mtl_apu.username,
mtl_apu.password,
mtl_apu.enabled,
mtl_apu.modified,
mtl_apu.created,
current_batch.batch_id
FROM $$raw_schema.adm_api_users mtl_apu
CROSS JOIN current_batch
ORDER BY
mtl_apu.username,
mtl_apu.created,
mtl_apu.modified;

object.customQuery:
SELECT
adm_api_users_row_id as adm_api_users_row_id,
adm_api_users_md5checksum as adm_api_users_md5checksum,
adm_api_users_batch_id as adm_api_users_batch_id,
user_name as user_name,
modified as modified,
adm_api_users_row_effective_end_datetime as adm_api_users_row_effective_end_datetime
FROM
$$staging_schema.adm_api_users
where
adm_api_users_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000';

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

fields.name: o_enabled
fields.expression:
-- 1. Convert 'enabled' field from STRING to INTEGER.
TO_INTEGER(enabled)

fields.name: o_Src_MD5
fields.expression:
MD5(
    'source_name' || source_name ||
    'load_type' || load_type ||
    'username' ||username ||
    'password' || password||
    'enabled' || enabled ||
    'modified' || modified ||
    'created' || created)

fields.name: o_insert_flag_record
fields.expression:
-- 1. Check if tgt_adm_commission_preview_row_id is null.
-- 2. Return 'I' if null, otherwise return 'X'.

IIF(ISNULL(tgt_adm_api_users_row_id), 'I', 'X')

fields.name: o_update_flag
fields.expression:
-- 1. Check if tgt_adm_api_users_row_id is NOT NULL.
-- 2. Compare o_Src_MD5 with tgt_adm_api_users_md5checksum.
-- 3. Return 'U' if both conditions are true, else 'X'.

IIF(NOT ISNULL(tgt_adm_api_users_row_id) AND o_Src_MD5 <> tgt_adm_api_users_md5checksum, 'U', 'X')

fields.name: o_end_datetime
fields.expression:
-- 1. Convert '9999-12-31' to DATETIME using TO_DATE function.
TO_DATE('9999-12-31', 'YYYY-MM-DD')
